      <title>卡罗琳·肯尼迪称表妹罗伯特·肯尼迪的疫苗观点很危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/caroline-kennedy-calls-cousin-rfk-jr-s-vaccine-views-dangerous</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻澳大利亚大使卡罗琳·肯尼迪称其堂兄罗伯特·F·肯尼迪对疫苗接种的看法“危险”，这是该家族资深成员对唐纳德·特朗普提名担任内阁要职的这位男士的最新一次公开谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/caroline-kennedy-calls-cousin-rfk-jr-s-vaccine-views-dangerous</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 04:07:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩誓言“无限制”增强核能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/kim-jong-un-vows-to-boost-nuclear-capabilities-without-limit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜官方媒体周一报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩誓言将“无限制”地增强国家核能力，以应对美国及其该地区盟友之间的安全伙伴关系所带来的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/kim-jong-un-vows-to-boost-nuclear-capabilities-without-limit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 03:05:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上田对暗示日本央行加息时机的谨慎态度导致日元走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/boj-s-ueda-says-timing-of-adjustment-depends-on-economy-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田一夫在备受关注的言论导致日元走弱之际，避免明确暗示将在 12 月会议上加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/boj-s-ueda-says-timing-of-adjustment-depends-on-economy-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:26:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命 FCC 资深人士 Brendan Carr 为该机构主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/trump-designates-fcc-veteran-brendan-carr-as-chair-of-agency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普在一份声明中表示，他已选择联邦通信委员会资深共和党人布伦丹·卡尔担任该委员会主席。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/trump-designates-fcc-veteran-brendan-carr-as-chair-of-agency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:20:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰盟友向泽连斯基施压，寻求结束战争的方法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/ukraine-war-latest-allies-are-leaning-on-zelenskiy-for-a-way-to-end-the-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在抵抗俄罗斯入侵近 1,000 天后，乌克兰的盟友正在敦促弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基考虑新的方式，以吸引弗拉基米尔·普京坐到谈判桌上，以寻求结束战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/ukraine-war-latest-allies-are-leaning-on-zelenskiy-for-a-way-to-end-the-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 22:19:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平向特朗普伸出橄榄枝的同时警告其红线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/xi-s-olive-branch-to-trump-comes-with-warning-on-china-red-lines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平利用与乔·拜登的最后一次会晤向唐纳德·特朗普发出明确信息：中国希望成为朋友，但如果有必要，也准备战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/xi-s-olive-branch-to-trump-comes-with-warning-on-china-red-lines</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 18:56:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国即将决定允许乌克兰袭击俄罗斯部分目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/us-nearing-decision-to-let-ukraine-hit-some-targets-in-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国即将做出最终决定，解除对乌克兰使用西方制造的武器袭击俄罗斯有限军事目标的一些限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/us-nearing-decision-to-let-ukraine-hit-some-targets-in-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 18:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普财政部内阁人选变动，竞争加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/bessent-spoke-with-musk-as-contest-endures-for-treasury-position</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的首席经济政策制定者的搜寻陷入混乱，竞争对手们争夺支持，助手们忙着寻找替代候选人，而候任总统对已经曝光在公众视野中的幕后争斗感到愤怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/bessent-spoke-with-musk-as-contest-endures-for-treasury-position</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 17:37:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国一周内发生第二起大规模杀戮事件；刺伤事件造成八人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/china-has-second-mass-killing-in-a-week-8-dead-in-stabbing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国东部江苏省发生持刀伤人事件，造成 8 人死亡，这是该国一周内发生的第二起大规模伤亡事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/china-has-second-mass-killing-in-a-week-8-dead-in-stabbing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 03:39:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
